Meet the course creator

I'm Jonathan Richardson, the creator of "AI in Business" course. I've always been a tech enthusiast and a forward-thinking entrepreneur. My journey into the world of AI began with a burning desire to revolutionize how businesses operate in a rapidly evolving landscape.

As a business owner myself, I've faced the challenges of staying competitive in a dynamic market. This firsthand experience propelled me to explore the transformative power of AI in driving business success. With a deep passion for innovation and a knack for simplifying complex concepts, I've made it my mission to make AI accessible to professionals from all walks of life.

My goal is to provide you with the knowledge and skills to thrive in the AI era, just as I have in my entrepreneurial journey.
